{"tid":2364380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制派議員終於識　要求逾200億東涌項目財委會分開表決","createTime":"2021-01-13T02:56:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T05:32:30.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2d27c99f3f363bcdcbbaefec8695847f3a568a","tid":2364380,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n（獨媒報導）上周立法會財委會，因為無議員提出要求在財委會分開表決，結果四個項目包括搬遷沙田污水處理廠、落馬洲河套地區發展、屯門中及錦田南建屋工程合共逾295億撥款申請，在無官員出席、沒有質詢的情況下「特快」獲得通過。立法會工務小組今日舉行會議，審議三個與東涌發展相關的項目合共233.8億撥款申請，建制派議員終於「覺醒」，在會上提出分開表決。今日兩小時會議亦通過古洞北57億供冷系統，兩項工程合共逾291億，「效率」極高。<br />\n<br />\n今日工務小組會議首先討論193.3億東涌西新市鎮擴展土地平整工程、1.3億研究大蠔至欣澳的P1公路以及39.1億區域供冷系統。計劃包括平整東涌西6公頃土地建屋、興建首階段2.5億東涌至大蠔的雙線公路、其他基建以及建設東涌西河畔公園及休憩用地等。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會麥美娟及熱血公民鄭松泰皆關注交通問題，鄭松泰認為低估了東涌使用私家車的比例。土木工程拓展署指目前北大嶼山公路不算擠塞，相信未來加上P1公路應足以應付。實政圓桌田北辰認為即便P1公路於2030年落成，與預計2036年落成的11號幹線有六個空檔，車流仍會塞回北青馬大橋，追問「係咪一條青馬大橋搞得掂？」直言「P1係廢嘅」，要求P1公路在財委會分開表決。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080164&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=55bc8571\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080164&h=fc4d8ad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080164</a>"},{"pid":"9582e790277a83908f5ec58920d29b9c2ab53d0f","tid":2364380,"uid":34409,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"分開表決唔係即係拉布咩？"},{"pid":"222fda98b45048802c9c955599db97e610dd3299","tid":2364380,"uid":40763,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:01:20.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},{"pid":"6f693b7e826dcb1c0d514f9c83206ce8e46b6bf7","tid":2364380,"uid":77905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:01:46.000Z","msg":"田北辰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲早都被反對派啦"},{"pid":"4727b6be1c363c42e350bf0ede6a1e0b8f83899d","tid":2364380,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:02:38.000Z","msg":"點解要分開?係唔係想反對政府?<br />\n國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925aaaeab99540881d01f95bce4a6c9873d93be7","tid":2364380,"uid":8762,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:05:47.000Z","msg":"全部拉布都犯國安，拉"},{"pid":"bc0ad6edcf53c56bb716d0f35ede41483ac14791","tid":2364380,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:16:25.000Z","msg":"松泰勁出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60cedc82092ad51720f406f935840d50256837c","tid":2364380,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:17:24.000Z","msg":"阻礙議會運作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38161d1292a8a7a7bd48d71b473615167db4b5c7","tid":2364380,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:18:19.000Z","msg":"原來仲未執嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05207a66a161f0ef9041ab3da45a02107a9225b","tid":2364380,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc0ad6edcf53c56bb716d0f35ede41483ac14791","tid":2364380,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:16:25.000Z","msg":"松泰勁出力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"扮演忠誠反對派嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}